0<\/li>\n\n<li>\u00a0Applying basic statistical methods to summarise\u00a0data<\/li>\n\n<li>Building statistical models<\/li>\n\n<li>Using R\u00a0for data\u00a0visualisation<\/li><\/ol><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Eligibility<\/strong><\/h2><ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>UG\/PG graduated students.<\/li>\n\n<li>Ph.D. Scholars from higher education institutes.<\/li>\n\n<li>Faculties \/ Staffs \/ Lab Instructors from technical and academic institutions.<\/li>\n\n<li>Industry\/working professionals seeking cyber security skills.<\/li>\n\n<li>Any other Cyber Security enthusiasts.<\/li><\/ul><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Important dates<\/strong><\/h2><ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><strong>Start Date:<\/strong> 19 May 2025<\/li>\n\n<li><strong>Duration:<\/strong> 6 days in-person + 9 online sessions<\/li>\n\n<li><strong>Tuition Fees:<\/strong> INR 20,000 (incl. GST)<\/li>\n\n<li><strong>Accommodation:<\/strong> INR 3,500 (food &amp; travel extra)<\/li>\n\n<li><strong>Note:<\/strong> GST rates may vary per government guidelines.<\/li>\n\n<li><strong>Apply Online:<\/strong> Submit your application by <strong>30 Mar 2025<\/strong>.<\/li>\n\n<li><strong>Written Test:<\/strong> Scheduled for <strong>06 Apr 2025<\/strong>.<\/li>\n\n<li><strong>Acceptance &amp; Fee Payment:<\/strong> Confirm by <strong>30 Apr 2025<\/strong>.<\/li>\n\n<li><strong>Onboarding:<\/strong> Starts <strong>10 May 2025<\/strong>.<\/li>\n\n<li><strong>Classes Begin:<\/strong> <strong>19 May 2025<\/strong>.<\/li><\/ul><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Registration<\/strong><\/h2><p>Interested candidates can register online via <a href=\"https:\/\/apply.azimpremjiuniversity.edu.in\/signup\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">this page<\/a>.<\/p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Financial Assistance<\/strong><\/h2><p>The University will extend financial assistance to deserving candidates based on their income, institutional affiliation, and other factors. This financial assistance could range from full fee waivers to partial waivers and will be awarded at the sole discretion of the University. The University will ask for documentary proof as&nbsp;required.<\/p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Learning Outcomes<\/strong><\/h2><ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Master quantitative analysis and data storytelling.<\/li>\n\n<li>Get skilled in R programming for statistical insights.<\/li>\n\n<li>Hybrid learning: 6 days in-person at Bengaluru + 9 online sessions.<\/li>\n\n<li>Accessible campus with wheelchair-friendly facilities and a cr\u00e8che for parents.<\/li><\/ul><h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https:\/\/azimpremjiuniversity.edu.in\/programmes\/certificate-in-quantitative-analysis-and-data-visualisation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>Clic khere to view the official notification of Certificate Course On Quantitative Analysis and Data Visualisation at Azim Premji University<\/strong><\/a><\/h4>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Applications are invited for Certificate Course On Quantitative Analysis and Data Visualisation at Azim Premji University. The last date of registration is 30 March. Course Overview Azim Premji University\u2019s Certificates Programme aims to enhance the capacity of the social sector in doing field research, analysing, interpreting data and writing about it. While the social sector [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":8,"featured_media":48397,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_crosspost_to_32":false,"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":"","_links_to":"","_links_to_target":""},"categories":[7931,8559],"tags":[],"states":[],"city":[],"category-filter":[],"headline-article":[],"class_list":["post-47953","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standar